Everything is there for you - outdoor pool with towel service, indoor pool, game room, bar, coffee shop and pizzeria right in hotel.	The lounge, pool bar and exercise room were fairly nice and easily accessible.	There is an indoor and outdoor pool, bars, and a spa.	I liked the indoor and outdoor pool area and the pool bar.	Both indoor and outdoor pool, game room, spa, and the beach was steps away!	The 2nd floor rooftop pool was fantastic with a full bar and towel service.